Package com.zanderwohl.chunks.World

Class Space

java.lang.Object
com.zanderwohl.chunks.World.Space
public class Space
extends java.lang.Object
Functions for converting world coordinates to Volume coordinates and vice-versa. World coordinates are the tuples representing a point in the world relative to that World's origin, and Volume coordinates are tuples that describe a location relative to a smaller Volume within the World.
